- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper's focus on solving PDEs using finite element methods is relevant to computational engineering and science. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation): The paper mentions the use of symbolic computation in the implementation of the new finite element transformations.
